data.description: Price Reduced! Move in ready. Start that new chapter in your new home.  Welcome to your new charming home on the outskirts of the vibrant Meridian life. As you walk in the front door, immerse yourself in an area primed for lasting memories to be built and shared. The main floor includes two family rooms, kitchen with breakfast bar, and one bedroom which is perfect as office, playroom, or guest room for all your friends to visit. Upstairs you will find the primary suite with a walk-in closet and two additional bedrooms. The backyard wraps around both sides of the house and is the perfect place for entertaining. The backyard playground invites giggles and squeals of delight as you enjoy the afternoon sun. Just a few houses down you will find the community pool for those hot summer days. There are plenty of parks and exploring paths for your enjoyment. New AC and furnace installed in 9/2021 and exterior paint 9/2022.
